# Oven-Cooked Cheese Macaroni

> This #american classic tastes great and cooks in the oven for easy, but sophisticated Mac & cheese

Preheat oven to 375°F

- Butter | 2 tbsp | 
- Cottage Cheese | 1 cup | 
- Milk | 2 cups | 
- Mustard (dry) | 1 tsp | 
- Cayenne | “Pinch” | 
- Nutmeg | “Pinch” | 
- Salt | 1/4 tsp | 
- Black Pepper | 1/4 tsp | 

Blend into purée

- Sharp Cheddar | 1 lb | 
- Elbow Noodles | 1/2 lb | 

Reserve 1/4 cup cheese, combine remaining ingredients

Pour into 9” square baking pan

Bake for 30 minutes

Add remaining cheese to top

Bake for 30 minutes more

